author: alexander.strecha@kurier.at (Alexander Strecha)
articleTitle: Copa Libertadores: Palmeiras holt den Titel
articleTitleTranslated: Copa Libertadores: Palmeiras takes the title
articleContent: Der brasilianische Rekordmeister schlug den FC Santos 1:0. Das Goldtor fiel in der 10.  Minute der Nachspielzeit.
articleContentTranslated: The Brazilian record champions beat FC Santos 1-0. The gold goal fell in the 10th minute of stoppage time.
